<i>noun</i>: 주거지 [주ː거지], 거처 [거처], 거주지 [거주지], 거주 [거주], 가옥 [가옥] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>주거지 [주ː거지]</dt><br>
<dd>residence; residential area; residential site</dd><br>
<dd>사람이 살고 있거나 살았던 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>A place where a person lives or used to live.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>거처 [거처]</dt><br>
<dd>residence; dwelling; abode</dd><br>
<dd>일정 기간 동안 자리를 잡고 머물러 사는 장소.</dd><br>
<dd>A place where people live for a certain amount of time.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>거주지 [거주지]</dt><br>
<dd>residence; abode; habitation</dd><br>
<dd>머물러 살고 있는 장소.</dd><br>
<dd>A place where people dwell and live.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>거주 [거주]</dt><br>
<dd>residence; habitation</dd><br>
<dd>일정한 곳에 머물러 삶.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of staying and living in a certain place.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가옥 [가옥]</dt><br>
<dd>home; house; residence</dd><br>
<dd>사람이 사는 집.</dd><br>
<dd>A building where people live.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>